data.description:
Welcome Home! This stunning ranch style home in the highly desirable neighborhood of Homestead at Sterling Ranch is ready for you to move in and begin experiencing serene living. Located in a quiet cul-de-sac on more than one quarter acre, this spacious residence offers custom features throughout, such as an oversized breakfast nook and an extended primary bedroom on the main floor, allowing your furniture to fit with ease, with an extra insulated wall to ensure quiet rest. Got dogs? The primary closet has a custom built-in dog door that leads to a gated off area in the garage and directly to the exterior dog run with synthetic turf! Speaking of garage, an extra 4 feet of garage space easily accommodates a full-size truck and offers plenty of overhead storage, which will remain with the home along with two overhead pulley systems for bicycles. The main living area allows natural light to flood in and highlight the upgraded luxury plank vinyl flooring while the spacious kitchen features a walk-in pantry, gas range, counter seating, granite countertops, canned lighting, stainless steel appliances, and upgraded fixtures. Head downstairs where you will find tall 9-foot ceilings, an extended open living space plumbed for a wet bar for entertaining or to sit while watching your favorite movies, and a Junior Primary Suite with an oversized shower and walk-in closet. The front of the home features an oversized 25' driveway for ample parking and a xeriscape yard while the backyard provides a cozy seating area under a covered patio with canned lighting, a converted grill connected directly to a gas line, a large shed with electrical access, a gated side yard, and hydraulic window well covers. The primary location allows for quick access to walking trails, open space, and parks, and is located in the Academy School District 20. This one is a must see!
OPEN HOUSE 4/6 & 4/7  11:00am-2:00 pm
